name: Bloom where you're planted— and die there
description:
M.M.I, pt 2: Suicide Ideation

The feeling of wanting to take your own life. While suicide ideation is feeling that even a person without mental illness can feel, it is cruelly overwhelming. 

Museum of Mental Incapabilities is a collection of artworks depicting mental health problems and disorders. Explore and understand what it feels like to live with various mental incapacities.

It may be difficult at times, you can still get on the road to feeling better.
